#, no-wrap
msgid "...-normal-r-normal-...-p-...\n"
msgstr "...-normal-r-normal-...-p-...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/articles/fonts/_index.adoc:280
msgid ""
"as the name, and then use man:xfontsel[1] to examine it and adjust the name "
